WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:09.000
Zach: I'm Zach. I'll teach you how real shops win while you choose the customers, equipment, people, and risks.

00:09.000 --> 00:18.000
Move your selected founder through the Garage Bay shop.

00:18.000 --> 00:27.000
Player: I actually cut the stock, set the CNC tools, checked the G code, and inspected my first part. Every step feels connected.

00:27.000 --> 00:36.000
Run the CNC program and verify the finished result.

00:36.000 --> 00:45.000
Complete a real production task and earn an A grade.
